<title>USA: Capri Corp six months net falls.</title>
<headline>Capri Corp six months net falls.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-02-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Capri Corp said Monday net income for the six-month period ended December 31 fell to $248,440, or about $0.02 a share, from from $794,035 reported in the same period one year ago.</p>
<p>Per share data for last year were not available.</p>
<p>Revenues in the period fell to $1.3 million from $1.9 million, the company said.</p>
<p>Capri said it remains optimistic about the next six months in spite of the drop in revenues.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
